MySQL Docker 이미지 다운로드
> docker pull mysql:8.0.17

Mysql Docker 실행
docker run -d -p 3306:3306 -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=password --name parksy-mysql -v /Users/parksy/datadir:/var/lib/mysql mysql:8.0.17 --character-set-server=utf8mb4 --collation-server=utf8mb4_unicode_ci

Mysql 서버 접속
> mysql -u root -p

유저 생성 및 권한 부여
mysql> CREATE USER 'parksy'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)

mysql> GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'parksy'@'%';
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)

mysql> flush privileges;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)

mysql> quit